title: Proposal to Boost the TRX-BNB Farm!
body:
**CAKE holders**, today we are thrilled to be able to offer you a new Syrup Pool from TRON, a public blockchain dedicated to providing the underlying infrastructure that enables developers to create smart contracts and decentralized applications, freely publish, own, and store data & other content.

# What is Boost?
Boost is basically an increase in farm multiplier over a set period of time, which is offered in exchange for additional tokens from the boosted project, which are then put into a new Syrup Pool!

So basically, TRX-BNB will go from a 1x multiple to a 2x multiple, which will last for 1 week, which will only cause temporary dilution among the other farms, and at the same time, there will be a new TRX Syrup Pool with $1M of tokens, to be earned by staking CAKE.



# The Syrup Pool:
Stake CAKE tokens to earn TRX tokens!

- **Total Tokens:** 16,700,000 TRX
- **Distribution duration:** 60 days
- **Start block:** 9202800 (approx. 9am UTC on July 16th)
- **Finish block:** 10930800 (approx. 9am UTC on September 14th)
- **Token rewards per block:** 9.6643 TRX


## Max Stake per wallet: 
100 CAKE for the first 48 hours, then unlimited CAKE staking afterwards. 

To give as many CAKE holders the opportunity to Farm some juicy pool rewards at a high APY, we will have a 100 CAKE token cap staking limit per user for the first 48 hours.

# What is TRON?

TRON is committed to promoting the decentralization of the Internet and is dedicated to building the infrastructure for a decentralized Internet.The TRON Protocol, one of the largest blockchain-based decentralized operating systems in the world, offers scalable, high-availability, and high-throughput support that serves as the foundation for all decentralized applications in the TRON ecosystem.The Protocol also uses an innovative, pluggable smart contract platform to improve compatibility with Ethereum smart contracts.



### To learn more about TRON, the chefs advise you to visit their official communication channels:

- **Website:** [https://tron.network/](https://tron.network/)
- **Twitter:** [https://twitter.com/Tronfoundation](https://twitter.com/Tronfoundation)
- **Telegram:** [https://t.me/tronnetworkEN](https://t.me/tronnetworkEN)

# How do you stake CAKE to earn TRX rewards?
If you own CAKE tokens, congratulations! You’re the master of your … pancakes.
Time to step up your taste buds by learning how to stake CAKE with Syrup Pool.
- Visit this webpage: [**https://pancakeswap.finance/syrup** ](https://pancakeswap.finance/syrup )
- Click “Approve CAKE” on the TRX Syrup Pool 
- Click on the stake button.
- Confirm the transaction.

BEP20 TRX will also be circulating and transferable on BSC when we start the Syrup pool, so you will be able to harvest your TRX tokens and trade on PancakeSwap at any time!



# BEWARE OF FOOD POISONING! ⚠️⚠️⚠️💀

The official TRX token contract address on Binance Smart Chain is:
[**https://bscscan.com/address/0x85eac5ac2f758618dfa09bdbe0cf174e7d574d5b**](https://bscscan.com/address/0x85eac5ac2f758618dfa09bdbe0cf174e7d574d5b)

Any other TRX token will be a scam and will result in a financial loss for users. Do not buy tokens from any other token address. Always verify the token address before purchasing tokens. If you receive airdrops from another address for TRX tokens, they will be rotten tokens (but not the cool kind!), and we advise you to ignore them.
